Steps it follows:

Read data from OMF

Check token and find backend

Validate order:

Shipping address exists

Email and phone are present

Order items exist and are correct

Products exist in Odoo

No duplicate items

If anything is wrong → send error message to OMF and refuse the order

If everything is okay → schedule job to import the order in Odoo

Send response back to OMF:

202 → order received

400 → validation error

401 → token missing or wrong
